
espeak:  espeak.sourceforge.net
  * higher available words/minute
  * easy key-binding;
      eg.: super+s = speak highlighted text



Fincur - financial figures
  A flexible ncurses application to finance.

  Purpose:
  - Easy browsing of transactions to allow for cherry-picking suspicious records
  - marking records for future purpose (eg, "bc" for business cost)
  - simple quantity/time reports. eg.: $30,000 in business costs/12 mths;
    $50,000 commute cost/6 mths
